Message<br>contents</FONT></TD>
<TD>
<TEXTAREA NAME="Text" COLS="60" ROWS="6" WRAP="VIRTUAL">First, you his the switch that brings you to the bottom of the purple block. Run all the way across, and you should see a red block. Juimp on to it from there. Then, hit the switch to the left of the screen to take you to the top of purple. You should see a yellow block, and a blue block. Next, take a long leap to yellow. Destroy the Aritfical Chaos, and then hit the gravity switch next to it. Hit the spring, and keep your control stick down. You will end up in a section with a rail, and a spring. Carefully, jump onto the rail, and grind over to green. Go up from there. You will encounter two spark beetles, but leave them alone so we can get along with this! You should find a sping that takes you back to purple. Once you find a path of rings, do a Light Dash to take you to blue. Hit the gravity switch, which will take you back to purple. Run across, then down, and you should find the switch whcih activates the missle! Take the gravity switch to red, run past the Aritifical Chaos, and pull the gravity switch behind the to indestrucable crates. Thiss will take you by the Goal Ring. Hit the switch, fire the missle and tag the ring! Hope this helps you! </TEXTAREA></TD>

